name: a user to user successful transaction -- @1.3
fullName: transaction: a user to user successful transaction

steps.name: Given there is user Alice in Ethereum network with the initial balance 100Ξ
And there is user Bob in Ethereum network with the initial balance 100Ξ
When user Alice sends 90Ξ to user Bob
Then the recipient has balance increased by 90Ξ
And the sender has balance decreased more than by 90Ξ
